com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.newaccounting

Class FiscalYearAccount

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.accounting.dataloader.newaccounting.FiscalYearAccount
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FiscalYearAccount>

    public class FiscalYearAccount
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<FiscalYearAccount>
    A Data Transfer Object that represents a link between a fiscal year and an account. The link specifies the account type and account group that contain the account in the year. The group has a relative order within the account type, and the account has a relative order within the account group. For a given fiscal year, the orderings produce a sortable ordering of the types, groups, and accounts useful in producing accounting statements.
    Author:
    Robert J. Muller
